# Title: one line, plain sentence, no tags (max 72 chars)

# --- Problem ---
# What was broken, missing, or needed? Why did this change need to happen?

# --- Solution ---
# How did we solve it? Key design decisions made.

# --- Flow / Behaviour Change (if any) ---
# How does the system behave differently now? Include before/after if useful.

# --- Env vars / Config (if any) ---
# New or changed env vars introduced by this change.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# Guidelines:
#   - Title: plain sentence, no feat:/fix:/chore: tags
#   - Keep each section short — bullets are fine
#   - Skip sections that don't apply (delete the header too)
#   - No "Co-Authored-By" lines
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
